\begin_layout Paragraph*
Alarms
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The system permits to define an alarm for each day of the week 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
From Monday to Friday.
 All the alarms are triggered at the same clock time.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Saturday and Sunday.
 Both alarms are triggered at the same time defined as a delay - measured
 in hours - from the alarms defined in 1.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
and a control of the alarm status: enabled/disabled.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
\emph on
Alarm 
\emph default
Data Entity
\end_layout

